Subject: [PATCH net-next v10 04/15] net: phy: Introduce PHY ports representation
Date: Tue, 22 Jul 2025 14:16:09 +0200
Message-ID: <20250722121623.609732-5-maxime.chevallier@bootlin.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.49.0
